snippet.textDisplay: I still remember renting this game as a kid at my local Blockbuster and being disappointed that I couldn't control the heroes, just the giant robot zords. The gameplay itself was also too stale/slow compared to other classic fighting games. The graphics were nice though and this theme would always stick out. Were you a Power Rangers fan as a kid (or now!)?

Back in the day I saw this game on a game's magazine and got really interested, the gameplay looked amazing. It wasn't all that I was expecting but I still had a lot of fun with it. I still remember the code to unlock Ivan Ooze haha.

And I liked Power Rangers as a kid, saw like the three first seasons and then lost interest.
